<subSubSection pageId="41" pageNumber="41" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="41.[701,1228,666,1274]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41">
COMMENTS: Rothschild did not designate a type in the original description, only saying that he had a good series. 
<bibRefCitation author="Rothschild, W. &amp; E. Hartert" pageId="41" pageNumber="41" pagination="85 - 205" refId="ref101261" refString="Rothschild, W., and E. Hartert. 1899. A review of the ornithology of the Galapagos Islands. With notes on the Webster - Harris Expedition. Novitates Zoologicae 6: 85 - 205, pls. V, VI." type="journal article" year="1899">Rothschild and Hartert (1899: 150)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned a series of 
<specimenCount pageId="41" pageNumber="41" type="generic">ten specimens</specimenCount>
from Wolf Island but still did not designate a type. 
<bibRefCitation author="Hartert, E." box="[903,1127,1019,1041]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41" pagination="123 - 178" refId="ref95790" refString="Hartert, E. 1919. Types of birds in the Tring Museum. B. Types in the general collection. Novitates Zoologicae 26: 123 - 178." type="journal article" year="1919">Hartert (1919: 172)</bibRefCitation>
listed as the type of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rothschild" authorityYear="1898" box="[861,920,1047,1070]" class="Aves" family="Thraupidae" genus="Certhidea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="41" pageNumber="41" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="becki">
<emphasis box="[861,920,1047,1070]" italics="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="41">becki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
male specimen no. 236 collected by Hull on Wenman Island on 
<date pageId="41" pageNumber="41" value="1897-07-31">31 July 1897</date>
, thereby designating it the 
<typeStatus box="[1115,1224,1106,1128]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41">lectotype</typeStatus>
. Of the 
<specimenCount box="[803,1042,1135,1157]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41" type="generic" typeStatus="paralectotypes">nine paralectotypes</specimenCount>
, the following six came to AMNH: 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="41" pageNumber="41">AMNH 522621– 522626</emphasis>
, 
<specimenCount box="[814,961,1194,1216]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41" type="male">three males</specimenCount>
and 
<specimenCount box="[1052,1223,1194,1216]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41" type="female">three females</specimenCount>
, collected on Wolf Island 
<date box="[1035,1200,1223,1245]" pageId="41" pageNumber="41" value="1897-07-31">31 July 1897</date>
– 
<date pageId="41" pageNumber="41" value="1897-08-04">4 August 1897</date>
.
</paragraph>
